high_descs: Go to the counter to the left.
Pick up the egg to the right of the plate on the counter.
Head left toward the white cupboard then turn right and go to the oven on the left.
Put the egg in the microwave, turn it on, and remove the egg.
Go right toward the sink and turn right, then go toward the wall and turn left at the garbage can.
Place the egg in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put egg in microwave and then throw it away.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk to the island.
Pick up the egg form the island.
Turn around to the left, walk around the island, and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the egg inside, close the microwave. Open the microwave, remove the egg, close the microwave.
Turn around to the right and walk to the trash bin the the right of the refrigerator.
Place the egg into the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm egg into a trash bin.

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the island on the right.
Pick up the egg from the center of the island.
Carry the egg and turn around, then right and face the stove on the left. Look up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the egg inside. Shut the door then open it. Take out the egg and shut the door.
Carry the egg and turn around and move all the way to the far wall. Turn left to face the trash can.
Place the egg in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Heat an egg and throw it away.
